es' Village\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The message comes a day after Paris Olympics supremo Tony Estanguet expressed a similar sentiment while playing down complaints from some residents and businesses about the impact of the event.\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The message\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar sentiment\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"complaints\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"some residents\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"businesses\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are ready as we head into the final phase,\\\" he told a press conference in Paris, five days from the opening ceremony on July 26.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.186711167590092e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final phase\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conf